title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1991-12-27
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6MHz) > dBpoweramp (WAV 24-bit/96k) > Samplitude Pro X5 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set I

They Love Each Other
Mama Tried >

Black Peter >

It's All Over Now, Baby Blue
